  "postcommunion": {
    "options": [
      {
        "body": {
          "lines": {
            "la": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Per huius virtútem sacraménti, quǽsumus, Dómine, beáti"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "exémplo, deduc nos iúgiter in tua dilectióne, et opus bonum quod cœpísti in nobis pérfice usque in diem Christi Iesu. Qui vivit et regnat in sǽcula sæculórum."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "es": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Te rogamos, Señor,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "por la eficacia de este sacramento y el ejemplo de san"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "que nos mantengas siempre en tu amor y lleves a su perfección hasta el día de Cristo Jesús la obra buena que has comenzado en nosotros."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Por Jesucristo, nuestro Señor."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "en-US": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "By the power of this Sacrament, Lord, we pray, lead us always in your love,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "through the example of blessed"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", and bring to fulfillment the good work you have begun in us until the day of Christ Jesus."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Who lives and reigns for ever and ever."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "it": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Per la forza di questo sacramento, sull’esempio di san"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "guidaci sempre, o Signore, nel tuo amore e porta a compimento fino al giorno di Cristo Gesù l’opera di bene che hai iniziato in noi. Per Cristo nostro Signore."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "fr": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Par la puissance de ce sacrement,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Seigneur, nous te prions :"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "conduis-nous sans cesse dans la voie de ton amour,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "comme tu fis pour saint(e)"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ";"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "l'œuvre de bonté que tu as entreprise en nous,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "poursuis-la jusqu’au jour du Christ Jésus."
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Lui qui vit et règne pour les siècles des siècles."
                }
              ]
            ],
            "de": [
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Allmächtiger Gott, du hast uns durch dieses Sakrament gestärkt. Lehre uns,"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "nach dem Beispiel des heiligen"
                },
                {
                  "type": "rubric",
                  "text": "N."
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "dich vor allem zu suchen und als neue Menschen in dieser Welt zu leben. Darum bitten wir durch Christus, unseren Herrn."
                }
              ]
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
